headline: Ally Financial Stock Up as It Rewards Shareholders With Buyback Plan
summary: ALLY jumps after unveiling a $2B multi-year share repurchase plan, signaling confidence, backed by strong liquidity and earnings momentum.

headline: Raymond James to Welcome New $692 Million Program with Bank Midwest
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., December 11, 2025--Raymond James announced today that Bank Midwest has selected its Financial Institutions Division (FID) to support the bank’s investment program.
